From the HN Tokyo hntokyo.io meetup last night. About a 100 people on the PARCO rooftop in Shibuya. Gorgeous view. Tons of new friends made. I got up an front of the group during announcements and declared myself a "Diplomat from HN Kansai and the OWDDM". Invited people to stop by if they ever come to Kansai. (Also big-upped Fukuoka as well... the _other_ Japan tech/startup group I am still in touch with)
